    public class PackingState
extends GraphStateImpl
    A packing state representing a certain arrangement of some rectangles within the container and possibly containing some remaining rectangles.
    Author:
    Przemysław Klęsk (wi.zut.edu.pl), Marcin Korzeń (wi.zut.edu.pl)
